  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Compare the analgesic effects of naproxen sodium codeine, paracetamol codeine and placebo on
      postoperative pain and tramadol (Contramal) consumption during the first 24 hour after a
      lumbar disk surgery.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Compare the analgesic effects of naproxen sodium codeine paracetamol codeine and placebo on
      postoperative pain intensity measured by the visual analogue scale, and evaluated tramadol
      consumption and related side effects.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
